dc_title_s: Height Modernization (ILHMP) LiDAR Data: Piatt County, Illinois: 2012
dc_description_s: This task order is for planning, acquisition, processing, and derivative products of LiDAR data to be collected for areas of Illinois. LiDAR data and derivative products produced in compliance with this task order are part of the data to be obtained under Job Number P-95-052-11. Specifications listed below are based on the U.S. Geological Survey National Geospatial Program Base LiDAR Specification, Version 13.
